台风盖伊以前所未有的强度吹袭泰国，在该国多个府的大范围地区构成破坏<ref name="GoTTC" />。春蓬府到[[罗勇府|罗勇府]]之间地区受到狂风暴雨和强烈涌浪的严重影响<ref name="HM1">{{cite news | work = [[路透社|Reuters]]| publisher = Hobart Mercury | date = 1989-11-08 | title = Captain stayed to fight storm | location = Bangkok, Thailand}} {{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。气旋经过期间，各地雨量以春蓬府最高，达194毫米<ref name="WPCMAX">{{cite book | last = Roth | first = David M. | date = 2015-04-30 | chapter = Tropical Cyclone Point Maxima | accessdate = 2015-09-06 | chapter-url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmaxima.html | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Data | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151022203526/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmaxima.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcrainfall.html | publisher = Weather Prediction Center | archivedate = 2015-10-22 }}</ref>。[[曼谷|曼谷]]以南大部分地区的通讯和供电发生故障，许多居民家中停电达数周之久<ref name="ReliefWeb">{{cite web | work = United Nations Department of Humanitarian Affairs | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 1989-11-21 | accessdate = 2016-02-08 | title = Thailand Typhoon Gay Nov 1989 UNDRO Information Report 1–4 | archivedate = 2015-11-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151109090118/http://reliefweb.int/report/thailand/thailand-typhoon-gay-nov-1989-undro-information-report-1-4 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/thailand/thailand-typhoon-gay-nov-1989-undro-information-report-1-4 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。破坏性的狂风将许多树木和电线杆连根拔起，还有许多建在支柱上的木质房屋被风推倒<ref name="HM2" />。风暴引起山洪暴发，灾情又因[[森林开伐|森林采伐]]加剧<ref name="DisasterReport" />，导致至少365人丧生，数以千计的民宅受损或被毁<ref name="SH1112">{{cite news | work = The Sun Herald | date = 1989-11-12 | title = 360 Die in Flash Floods; Thailand | page = 9 | location = Sydney, Australia}} {{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。春蓬府各地多个城镇和村庄变得满目苍痍，《[[曼谷邮报|曼谷邮报]]》报道称其中一个被毁的村庄“看上去仿佛遭受过轰炸”<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = [[悉尼先驱晨报|Sydney Morning Herald]] | date = 1989-11-06 | title = Typhoon Brings Mayhem | page = 14 | location = Bangkok, Thailand}} {{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。另据报道，春蓬府和[[班武里府|班武里府]]有多个社区完全被“夷平”<ref name="HM2">{{cite news | agency = Agence France-Presse | newspaper = Hobart Mercury | date = 1989-11-07 | title = Frantic hunt for victims of Thai typhoon | location = Bangkok, Thailand}} {{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。春蓬府和[[素叻府|素叻府]]各地有许多学校被台风摧毁，其中大部分都是木质建筑。风暴行进路途附近所有建筑物的窗户和门都被狂风刮跑，一些多层建筑的上层也不复存在。少数以钢筋混凝土建造的学校所受破坏程度较轻。<ref name="1996rpt">{{cite web | publisher = United Nations Educational, Scientific and Cultural Organization | year = 1996 | accessdate = 2016-02-08 | title = Multi-Purpose Buildings for Disaster Situations in Thailand | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131021140859/http://apfeiu.unescoapceiu.org/pdf/rud_05.pdf | archivedate = 2013-10-21 | url = http://apfeiu.unescoapceiu.org/pdf/rud_05.pdf | format = PDF | author = Kriangsak Charanyanond }}</ref>台风沿途有上千条道路和194座桥梁受损或被冲毁<ref name="DisasterReport" />，引发的洪灾一度导致超过25万公顷土地被淹<ref name="RemoteSensing" />。盖伊在陆地上一共夺走558条人命，近海另有44人丧生<ref name="DisasterReport" />。整个泰国有约4万7000套民宅受损或被毁，超过20万人受到影响，其中约有15万3000人流离失所<ref name="DisasterReport" /><ref name="RemoteSensing">{{cite web | author = Manu Omakupt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131021142703/http://www.isprs.org/proceedings/XXIX/congress/part7/744_XXIX-part7.pdf | publisher = International Society for Photogrammetry and Remote Sensing | date = 1992-08 | accessdate = 2016-02-08 | title = Application of Remote Sensing and GIS for Renewable Resources Damaged by Typhoon 'Gay': Chumphon Province | url = http://www.isprs.org/proceedings/XXIX/congress/part7/744_XXIX-part7.pdf | format = PDF | location = Thailand | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-10-21 }}</ref>。全国遭受的经济损失达110亿[[泰铢|泰铢]]（1989年泰铢，相当于同年的4亿5650万美元），盖伊因此成为该国历史上造成破坏最严重的灾难之一<ref name="ADRC">{{cite web | publisher = Asian Disaster Reduction Center | year = 1998 | accessdate = 2016-02-08 | title = Thailand Country Report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131022174840/http://www.adrc.asia/countryreport/THA/THAeng98/index.html | archivedate = 2013-10-22 | url = http://www.adrc.asia/countryreport/THA/THAeng98/index.html }}</ref>。

气旋过去不到一周后，泰国政府开始向各灾区居民发放救灾物资<ref name="ReliefWeb" />。11月9日，来自[[达塞渡县|达塞渡县]]等地的约2500人举行示威，要求政府提供更多物资，但很快就被驱散<ref>{{cite news | agency = Agence France-Presse | newspaper = Hobart Mercury | date = 1989-11-09 | title = Rage of typhoon victims | location = Bangkok, Thailand}} {{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。泰国政府对台风影响轻描淡写的做法引来大量批评，[[泰国总理|总理]][[差猜·春哈旺|差猜·春哈旺]]因此推迟对美国的访问，亲自督导救灾工作<ref name="SH1112" />。到11月15日时，美国已承诺捐款2万5000美元用于救灾。此时曼谷到巴蜀之间的电话已经接通，但更南部的地区仍未恢复。由于春蓬府大部分地区的停电情况持续了超过两周，因此当地医院和政府机构只能利用发电机来保持运作。随着破坏程度逐渐明朗，泰国政府于11月17日向联合国救灾机构请求国际援助。请求发出后，有6个国家承诺会一起提供近51万美元资金。<ref name="DisasterReport" /><ref name="ReliefWeb" />素叻府各地农业也因这场台风受到长期性的沉重打击。气旋过去后的4年里，作为果园、橡胶和油棕种植园的土地从33.32%降低到30.53%。此外，水稻种植覆盖率也从22.96%下降到13.03个百分点。<ref>{{cite web |author1=Absornsuda Siripong |author2=Wish Siripong |author3=Takashige Sugimoto |publisher=Chulalongkorn University Faculty of Science, Department of Marine Science |year=1997 |accessdate=2016-02-08 |title=Landuse changes at Surat Thani, Southern Thailand from 1973 to 1993 |url=http://agris.fao.org/agris-search/search.do?recordID=TH2000003360 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021144315/http://agris.fao.org/agris-search/search/display.do?f=2002%2FTH%2FTH02005.xml%3BTH2000003360 |archivedate=2013-10-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

盖伊过去后举行的调查表明，大部分受损严重的学校修筑方式存在问题，并且上层楼房也不能抵御台风强度风力。根据泰国建筑法规，所有建筑物都必须能够承受每平方米120[[千克力|千克力]]的风力。台风过去后的数年里，许多工程师在受灾最严重的区域开展研究，以求找到重建该国建筑物的最佳途径。许多被毁建筑都是木质，因此有关部门建议以钢筋混凝土重建。只要修筑方法得当，新的建筑物可能屹立50年不倒，但还是有不合规范的建筑物需要在5年内整修。<ref name="1996rpt" />

===印度===
穿越马来半岛后，台风盖伊于11月6日经过[[安达曼群岛|安达曼群岛]]。出于安全起见，当地所有海上和空中交通均予暂停。[[北安达曼岛|北安达曼岛]]受到时速超过120公里的狂风冲击，致使两幢建筑倒塌。<ref name="Andaman" />台风登陆数天前，[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]官员开始疏散沿海地区约5万居民并储存救援物资，[[维沙卡帕特南县|维沙卡帕特南县]]和[[斯里加古兰县|斯里加古兰县]]部分易受影响地区的居民被强制撤离<ref>{{cite news | agency = United Press International | newspaper = The Vindicator | date = 1989-11-09 | accessdate = 2011-12-17 | title = Typhoon's toll: some 200 dead, 20,000 homeless | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=2ixKAAAAIBAJ&sjid=1oUMAAAAIBAJ&dq=nellore+prakasam+cyclone&pg=2884,4648398&hl=zh-CN | page = 36 | archive-date = 2021-02-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210217041201/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=2ixKAAAAIBAJ&sjid=1oUMAAAAIBAJ&dq=nellore+prakasam+cyclone&pg=2884%2C4648398&hl=zh-CN | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | agency = United Press International | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | location = Bangkok, Thailand | date = 1989-11-09 | accessdate = 2016-02-08 | title = Typhoon Threatens Crowded Coast of India | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1989-11-09/news/mn-1447_1_crowded-coast | archivedate = 2015-02-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150225134120/http://articles.latimes.com/1989-11-09/news/mn-1447_1_crowded-coast | deadurl = no }}</ref>。当地多名[[气象学|气象学家]]警告，风暴可以同[[1977年安德拉邦气旋|1977年那场夺走上万条人命的气旋]]相提并论<ref>{{cite news | author = Paul Wedel | publisher = United Press International | date = 1989-11-08 | title = Typhoon Gay heads toward India | location = Bangkok, Thailand}} {{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。吹袭安德拉邦南海岸期间，盖伊产生时速高达320公里的强烈阵风<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = [[卫报|The Guardian]] | location = London, England | date = 1989-11-14 | title = Weather World: India hit by 200mph winds}} {{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。沿海出现3.5米高的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]，淹没的地区距原有海岸线还有3公里，许多建筑被水冲走<ref name="AMS2003" /><ref>{{cite web | author = A. D. Rao | publisher = Centre for Atmospheric Sciences | date = 2006-11 | accessdate = 2016-02-08 | title = On recent developments in storm surge inundation modelling | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130512121159/http://nidm.gov.in/idmc2/PDF/Presentations/Cyclone/Pres2.pdf | archivedate = 2013-05-12 | url = http://nidm.gov.in/idmc2/PDF/Presentations/Cyclone/Pres2.pdf | format = PDF }}</ref>。[[卡瓦利|卡瓦利]]城外约20公里处有座91米高的钢格[[微波通讯|微波塔]]倒塌，估计刮倒该塔的狂风时速为142公里<ref>{{cite journal | author = A. Abraham | author2 = P. Harikrishna | author3 = S. Gomathinayagam | author4 = N. Lakshmanan | journal = Journal of Structural Engineering | date = 2005-09 | title = Failure investigation of microwave towers during cyclones — A case study | volume = 32 | issue = 3 | pages = 147–157}}</ref>。安得拉邦南部各地的交通和通讯受阻，约2万套民房受损或被毁，导致至少10万人无家可归<ref>{{cite news | agency = Reuters | newspaper = [[洛杉矶时报|Los Angeles Times]] | location = [[洛杉矶|Los Angeles]], [[加利福尼亚州|California]] | date = 1989-11-11 | accessdate = 2016-02-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150225134007/http://articles.latimes.com/1989-11-11/news/mn-1002_1_death-toll | deadurl = no | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1989-11-11/news/mn-1002_1_death-toll | title = Typhoon Death Toll Rises; 500 Missing Off Thailand Coast | archivedate = 2015-02-25 }}</ref>。安纳加里帕林（{{lang|en|Annagaripalem}}）几乎所有的建筑物不是被毁就是严重受损<ref name="CourtCase" />。[[默苏利珀德姆|默苏利珀德姆]]近海有25名拒绝听从警告返回港口的渔夫溺毙<ref>{{cite news | publisher = Associated Press | date = 1989-11-09 | title = Cyclone Kills 25 | location = New Delhi, India}} {{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。安德拉邦各地共因这场台风导致69人遇难，经济损失约4.1亿[[印度卢比|印度卢比]]（1989年印度卢比，相当于同年的2527万美元）<ref name="AMS2003" /><ref>{{cite web | publisher = India Meteorological Department | year = 1999 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150717083945/http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/static/cyclone-history-bb.htm | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | title = Historical records of Severe Cyclones which formed in the Bay of Bengal and made landfall at the eastern coast of India during the period from 1970–1999 | url = http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/static/cyclone-history-bb.htm | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2015-07-17 }}</ref>。风暴过去后的几个月里，当地用混凝土建成多个避难所，用于安署流离失所的灾民<ref name="CourtCase">{{cite web | publisher = Orders of Joint Collector | date = 2009-12-12 | accessdate = 2012-04-23 | title = Case No.E5/3311/2009 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120423115820/http://nellore.ap.nic.in/jccourt/Assignment/E5_3311_2009.doc | deadurl = yes | url = http://nellore.ap.nic.in/jccourt/Assignment/E5_3311_2009.doc | format = .DOC | archivedate = 2012-04-23 }}</ref>。

